{
  "stem": "5516.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they find a pack of cigarettes, they hanged one man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They find a pack of cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You could do it if they don't find it, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to bring in, in the ghetto, you cannot bring in nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was Lithuanian police, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They was-- before the war, they was acting like friends, brothers, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No brothers, but friends, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when the German come in, before they had the orders, they start to kill the Jews on their own.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And even the German-- when the army comes in, a German army comes in, they go, and they fight, and they come in our city.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Shavel, they come in, in Siauliai.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a field commandant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He come in, and he was ruling for a few days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After this he goes, again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He's go on the way to Russia, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But in the few days where he says there, before he come in, the Lithuanian people started to go in the Jewish places and kill them, and take all the stuff, and they used to drag the bundles.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Till he find out, he didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He send out the German army to stop this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But when a few days later when he goes out, then the SS comes in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then they come in and they started to rule us already with the Jewish population, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some were stranger, but we know each another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even I wasn't too long a citizen of this city, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the same, I know a lot of people there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I think we had-- we couldn't have money at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not allowed to have money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in the ghetto, they took away-- they put tables, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
